101#define PREFIX_PARAMETERS "%p - [webFrame=%p, webFrameID=%" PRIu64 ", webPage=%p, webPageID=%" PRIu64 "] WebFrameLoaderClient::"
102#define WEBFRAME (&webFrame())
103#define WEBFRAMEID (webFrame().frameID().toUInt64())
104#define WEBPAGE (webFrame().page())
105#define WEBPAGEID (WEBPAGE ? WEBPAGE->identifier().toUInt64() : 0)
106
107#define WEBFRAMELOADERCLIENT_RELEASE_LOG(channel, fmt, ...) RELEASE_LOG(channel, PREFIX_PARAMETERS fmt, this, WEBFRAME, WEBFRAMEID, WEBPAGE, WEBPAGEID, ##__VA_ARGS__)
108#define WEBFRAMELOADERCLIENT_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(channel, fmt, ...) RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(channel, PREFIX_PARAMETERS fmt, this, WEBFRAME, WEBFRAMEID, WEBPAGE, WEBPAGEID, ##__VA_ARGS__)
109#define WEBFRAMELOADERCLIENT_RELEASE_LOG_FAULT(channel, fmt, ...) RELEASE_LOG_FAULT(channel, PREFIX_PARAMETERS fmt, this, WEBFRAME, WEBFRAMEID, WEBPAGE, WEBPAGEID, ##__VA_ARGS__)

116{
117}

119WebFrameLoaderClient::~WebFrameLoaderClient()
120{
121 m_frame->invalidate();
122}

198void WebFrameLoaderClient::detachedFromParent2()
199{
200 WebPage* webPage = m_frame->page();
201 if (!webPage)
202 return;
203
204#if ENABLE(RESOURCE_LOAD_STATISTICS)
205 if (m_frameSpecificStorageAccessIdentifier) {
206 WebProcess::singleton().ensureNetworkProcessConnection().connection().send(Messages::NetworkConnectionToWebProcess::RemoveStorageAccessForFrame(
207 m_frameSpecificStorageAccessIdentifier->frameID, m_frameSpecificStorageAccessIdentifier->pageID), 0);
208 m_frameSpecificStorageAccessIdentifier = std::nullopt;
209 }
210#endif
211
212 RefPtr<API::Object> userData;
213
214 // Notify the bundle client.
215 webPage->injectedBundleLoaderClient().didRemoveFrameFromHierarchy(*webPage, m_frame, userData);
216}

222
223void WebFrameLoaderClient::assignIdentifierToInitialRequest(unsigned long identifier, DocumentLoader* loader, const ResourceRequest& request)
224{
225 WebPage* webPage = m_frame->page();
226 if (!webPage)
227 return;
228
229 bool pageIsProvisionallyLoading = false;
230 if (FrameLoader* frameLoader = loader ? loader->frameLoader() : nullptr)
231 pageIsProvisionallyLoading = frameLoader->provisionalDocumentLoader() == loader;
232
233 webPage->injectedBundleResourceLoadClient().didInitiateLoadForResource(*webPage, m_frame, identifier, request, pageIsProvisionallyLoading);
234 webPage->addResourceRequest(identifier, request);
235}
236
237void WebFrameLoaderClient::dispatchWillSendRequest(DocumentLoader*, unsigned long identifier, ResourceRequest& request, const ResourceResponse& redirectResponse)
238{
239 WebPage* webPage = m_frame->page();
240 if (!webPage)
241 return;
242
243 // The API can return a completely new request. We should ensure that at least the requester
244 // is kept, so that if this is a main resource load it's still considered as such.
245 auto requester = request.requester();
246 auto appBoundValue = request.isAppBound();
247 webPage->injectedBundleResourceLoadClient().willSendRequestForFrame(*webPage, m_frame, identifier, request, redirectResponse);
248 if (!request.isNull()) {
249 request.setRequester(requester);
250 request.setIsAppBound(appBoundValue);
251 }
252}

341void WebFrameLoaderClient::dispatchDidReceiveServerRedirectForProvisionalLoad()
342{
343 WebPage* webPage = m_frame->page();
344 if (!webPage)
345 return;
346
347 WebDocumentLoader* documentLoader = static_cast<WebDocumentLoader*>(m_frame->coreFrame()->loader().provisionalDocumentLoader());
348 if (!documentLoader) {
349 WEBFRAMELOADERCLIENT_RELEASE_LOG_FAULT(Loading, "dispatchDidReceiveServerRedirectForProvisionalLoad: Called with no provisional DocumentLoader (frameState=%hhu, stateForDebugging=%i)", m_frame->coreFrame()->loader().state(), m_frame->coreFrame()->loader().stateMachine().stateForDebugging());
350 return;
351 }
352
353 RefPtr<API::Object> userData;
354
355 LOG(Loading, "WebProcess %i - dispatchDidReceiveServerRedirectForProvisionalLoad to request url %s", getCurrentProcessID(), documentLoader->request().url().string().utf8().data());
356
357 // Notify the bundle client.
358 webPage->injectedBundleLoaderClient().didReceiveServerRedirectForProvisionalLoadForFrame(*webPage, m_frame, userData);
359
360 // Notify the UIProcess.
361 webPage->send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidReceiveServerRedirectForProvisionalLoadForFrame(m_frame->frameID(), documentLoader->navigationID(), documentLoader->request(), UserData(WebProcess::singleton().transformObjectsToHandles(userData.get()).get())));
362}

426void WebFrameLoaderClient::dispatchWillChangeDocument(const URL& currentUrl, const URL& newUrl)
427{
428#if ENABLE(RESOURCE_LOAD_STATISTICS)
429 if (m_frame->isMainFrame())
430 return;
431
432 WebPage* webPage = m_frame->page();
433 if (!webPage)
434 return;
435
436 if (m_frameSpecificStorageAccessIdentifier && !WebCore::areRegistrableDomainsEqual(currentUrl, newUrl)) {
437 WebProcess::singleton().ensureNetworkProcessConnection().connection().send(Messages::NetworkConnectionToWebProcess::RemoveStorageAccessForFrame(
438 m_frameSpecificStorageAccessIdentifier->frameID, m_frameSpecificStorageAccessIdentifier->pageID), 0);
439 m_frameSpecificStorageAccessIdentifier = std::nullopt;
440 }
441#endif
442}

509
510void WebFrameLoaderClient::dispatchDidStartProvisionalLoad()
511{
512 WebPage* webPage = m_frame->page();
513 if (!webPage)
514 return;
515
516#if ENABLE(FULLSCREEN_API)
517 Element* documentElement = m_frame->coreFrame()->document()->documentElement();
518 if (documentElement && documentElement->containsFullScreenElement())
519 webPage->fullScreenManager()->exitFullScreenForElement(webPage->fullScreenManager()->element());
520#endif
521
522 webPage->findController().hideFindUI();
523 webPage->sandboxExtensionTracker().didStartProvisionalLoad(m_frame.ptr());
524
525
526 RefPtr<API::Object> userData;
527
528 // Notify the bundle client.
529 webPage->injectedBundleLoaderClient().didStartProvisionalLoadForFrame(*webPage, m_frame, userData);
530 RefPtr provisionalLoader = static_cast<WebDocumentLoader*>(m_frame->coreFrame()->loader().provisionalDocumentLoader());
531
532 if (!provisionalLoader)
533 return;
534
535 auto& url = provisionalLoader->url();
536 auto& unreachableURL = provisionalLoader->unreachableURL();
537 // Notify the UIProcess.
538 webPage->send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidStartProvisionalLoadForFrame(m_frame->frameID(), m_frame->info(), provisionalLoader->request(), provisionalLoader->navigationID(), url, unreachableURL, UserData(WebProcess::singleton().transformObjectsToHandles(userData.get()).get())));
539}

541static constexpr unsigned maxTitleLength = 1000; // Closest power of 10 above the W3C recommendation for Title length.
542
543void WebFrameLoaderClient::dispatchDidReceiveTitle(const StringWithDirection& title)
544{
545 WebPage* webPage = m_frame->page();
546 if (!webPage)
547 return;
548
549 auto truncatedTitle = truncateFromEnd(title, maxTitleLength);
550
551 RefPtr<API::Object> userData;
552
553 // Notify the bundle client.
554 // FIXME: Use direction of title.
555 webPage->injectedBundleLoaderClient().didReceiveTitleForFrame(*webPage, truncatedTitle.string, m_frame, userData);
556
557 // Notify the UIProcess.
558 webPage->send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidReceiveTitleForFrame(m_frame->frameID(), truncatedTitle.string, UserData(WebProcess::singleton().transformObjectsToHandles(userData.get()).get())));
559}
560
561void WebFrameLoaderClient::dispatchDidCommitLoad(std::optional<HasInsecureContent> hasInsecureContent, std::optional<UsedLegacyTLS> usedLegacyTLSFromPageCache)
562{
563 WebPage* webPage = m_frame->page();
564 if (!webPage)
565 return;
566
567 WebDocumentLoader& documentLoader = static_cast<WebDocumentLoader&>(*m_frame->coreFrame()->loader().documentLoader());
568 RefPtr<API::Object> userData;
569
570 // Notify the bundle client.
571 webPage->injectedBundleLoaderClient().didCommitLoadForFrame(*webPage, m_frame, userData);
572
573 webPage->sandboxExtensionTracker().didCommitProvisionalLoad(m_frame.ptr());
574
575 bool usedLegacyTLS = documentLoader.response().usedLegacyTLS();
576 if (!usedLegacyTLS && usedLegacyTLSFromPageCache)
577 usedLegacyTLS = usedLegacyTLSFromPageCache == UsedLegacyTLS::Yes;
578
579 // Notify the UIProcess.
580 webPage->send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidCommitLoadForFrame(m_frame->frameID(), m_frame->info(), documentLoader.request(), documentLoader.navigationID(), documentLoader.response().mimeType(), m_frameHasCustomContentProvider, m_frame->coreFrame()->loader().loadType(), valueOrCompute(documentLoader.response().certificateInfo(), [] { return CertificateInfo(); }), usedLegacyTLS, m_frame->coreFrame()->document()->isPluginDocument(), hasInsecureContent, documentLoader.mouseEventPolicy(), UserData(WebProcess::singleton().transformObjectsToHandles(userData.get()).get())));
581 webPage->didCommitLoad(m_frame.ptr());
582}
583
584void WebFrameLoaderClient::dispatchDidFailProvisionalLoad(const ResourceError& error, WillContinueLoading willContinueLoading)
585{
586 WebPage* webPage = m_frame->page();
587 if (!webPage)
588 return;
589
590 WEBFRAMELOADERCLIENT_RELEASE_LOG(Network, "dispatchDidFailProvisionalLoad:");
591
592 RefPtr<API::Object> userData;
593
594 // Notify the bundle client.
595 webPage->injectedBundleLoaderClient().didFailProvisionalLoadWithErrorForFrame(*webPage, m_frame, error, userData);
596
597 webPage->sandboxExtensionTracker().didFailProvisionalLoad(m_frame.ptr());
598
599 // FIXME: This is gross. This is necessary because if the client calls WKBundlePageStopLoading() from within the didFailProvisionalLoadWithErrorForFrame
600 // injected bundle client call, that will cause the provisional DocumentLoader to be disconnected from the Frame, and didDistroyNavigation message
601 // to be sent to the UIProcess (and the destruction of the DocumentLoader). If that happens, and we had captured the navigationID before injected bundle
602 // client call, the DidFailProvisionalLoadForFrame would send a navigationID of a destroyed Navigation, and the UIProcess would not be able to find it
603 // in its table.
604 //
605 // A better solution to this problem would be find a clean way to postpone the disconnection of the DocumentLoader from the Frame until
606 // the entire FrameLoaderClient function was complete.
607 uint64_t navigationID = 0;
608 ResourceRequest request;
609 if (auto documentLoader = m_frame->coreFrame()->loader().provisionalDocumentLoader()) {
610 navigationID = static_cast<WebDocumentLoader*>(documentLoader)->navigationID();
611 request = documentLoader->request();
612 }
613
614 // Notify the UIProcess.
615 WebCore::Frame* coreFrame = m_frame->coreFrame();
616 webPage->send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidFailProvisionalLoadForFrame(m_frame->frameID(), m_frame->info(), request, navigationID, coreFrame->loader().provisionalLoadErrorBeingHandledURL().string(), error, willContinueLoading, UserData(WebProcess::singleton().transformObjectsToHandles(userData.get()).get())));
617
618 // If we have a load listener, notify it.
619 if (WebFrame::LoadListener* loadListener = m_frame->loadListener())
620 loadListener->didFailLoad(m_frame.ptr(), error.isCancellation());
621}
622
623void WebFrameLoaderClient::dispatchDidFailLoad(const ResourceError& error)
624{
625 WebPage* webPage = m_frame->page();
626 if (!webPage)
627 return;
628
629 WEBFRAMELOADERCLIENT_RELEASE_LOG(Network, "dispatchDidFailLoad:");
630
631 RefPtr<API::Object> userData;
632
633 auto& documentLoader = static_cast<WebDocumentLoader&>(*m_frame->coreFrame()->loader().documentLoader());
634 auto navigationID = documentLoader.navigationID();
635
636 // Notify the bundle client.
637 webPage->injectedBundleLoaderClient().didFailLoadWithErrorForFrame(*webPage, m_frame, error, userData);
638
639 // Notify the UIProcess.
640 webPage->send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidFailLoadForFrame(m_frame->frameID(), m_frame->info(), documentLoader.request(), navigationID, error, UserData(WebProcess::singleton().transformObjectsToHandles(userData.get()).get())));
641
642 // If we have a load listener, notify it.
643 if (WebFrame::LoadListener* loadListener = m_frame->loadListener())
644 loadListener->didFailLoad(m_frame.ptr(), error.isCancellation());
645}
646
647void WebFrameLoaderClient::dispatchDidFinishDocumentLoad()
648{
649 WebPage* webPage = m_frame->page();
650 if (!webPage)
651 return;
652
653 RefPtr<API::Object> userData;
654
655 auto navigationID = static_cast<WebDocumentLoader&>(*m_frame->coreFrame()->loader().documentLoader()).navigationID();
656
657 // Notify the bundle client.
658 webPage->injectedBundleLoaderClient().didFinishDocumentLoadForFrame(*webPage, m_frame, userData);
659
660 // Notify the UIProcess.
661 webPage->send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidFinishDocumentLoadForFrame(m_frame->frameID(), navigationID, UserData(WebProcess::singleton().transformObjectsToHandles(userData.get()).get())));
662
663 webPage->didFinishDocumentLoad(m_frame);
664}
665
666void WebFrameLoaderClient::dispatchDidFinishLoad()
667{
668 WebPage* webPage = m_frame->page();
669 if (!webPage)
670 return;
671
672 RefPtr<API::Object> userData;
673
674 auto& documentLoader = static_cast<WebDocumentLoader&>(*m_frame->coreFrame()->loader().documentLoader());
675 auto navigationID = documentLoader.navigationID();
676
677 // Notify the bundle client.
678 webPage->injectedBundleLoaderClient().didFinishLoadForFrame(*webPage, m_frame, userData);
679
680 // Notify the UIProcess.
681 webPage->send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidFinishLoadForFrame(m_frame->frameID(), m_frame->info(), documentLoader.request(), navigationID, UserData(WebProcess::singleton().transformObjectsToHandles(userData.get()).get())));
682
683 // If we have a load listener, notify it.
684 if (WebFrame::LoadListener* loadListener = m_frame->loadListener())
685 loadListener->didFinishLoad(m_frame.ptr());
686
687 webPage->didFinishLoad(m_frame);
688}

690void WebFrameLoaderClient::completePageTransitionIfNeeded()
691{
692 if (m_didCompletePageTransition)
693 return;
694
695 auto* webPage = m_frame->page();
696 if (!webPage)
697 return;
698
699 webPage->didCompletePageTransition();
700 m_didCompletePageTransition = true;
701 WEBFRAMELOADERCLIENT_RELEASE_LOG(Layout, "completePageTransitionIfNeeded: dispatching didCompletePageTransition");
702}
703
704void WebFrameLoaderClient::dispatchDidReachLayoutMilestone(OptionSet<WebCore::LayoutMilestone> milestones)
705{
706 WebPage* webPage = m_frame->page();
707 if (!webPage)
708 return;
709
710 RefPtr<API::Object> userData;
711
712 if (milestones & DidFirstLayout) {
713 WEBFRAMELOADERCLIENT_RELEASE_LOG(Layout, "dispatchDidReachLayoutMilestone: dispatching DidFirstLayoutForFrame");
714
715 // FIXME: We should consider removing the old didFirstLayout API since this is doing double duty with the
716 // new didLayout API.
717 webPage->injectedBundleLoaderClient().didFirstLayoutForFrame(*webPage, m_frame, userData);
718 webPage->send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidFirstLayoutForFrame(m_frame->frameID(), UserData(WebProcess::singleton().transformObjectsToHandles(userData.get()).get())));
719
720#if USE(COORDINATED_GRAPHICS)
721 // Make sure viewport properties are dispatched on the main frame by the time the first layout happens.
722 ASSERT(!webPage->useFixedLayout() || m_frame.ptr() != &m_frame->page()->mainWebFrame() || m_frame->coreFrame()->document()->didDispatchViewportPropertiesChanged());
723#endif
724 }
725
726#if !RELEASE_LOG_DISABLED
727 StringBuilder builder;
728 auto addIfSet = [&milestones, &builder] (WebCore::LayoutMilestone milestone, const String& toAdd) {
729 if (milestones.contains(milestone)) {
730 if (!builder.isEmpty())
731 builder.append(", ");
732 builder.append(toAdd);
733 }
734 };
735
736 addIfSet(DidFirstLayout, "DidFirstLayout"_s);
737 addIfSet(DidFirstVisuallyNonEmptyLayout, "DidFirstVisuallyNonEmptyLayout"_s);
738 addIfSet(DidHitRelevantRepaintedObjectsAreaThreshold, "DidHitRelevantRepaintedObjectsAreaThreshold"_s);
739 addIfSet(DidFirstFlushForHeaderLayer, "DidFirstFlushForHeaderLayer"_s);
740 addIfSet(DidFirstLayoutAfterSuppressedIncrementalRendering, "DidFirstLayoutAfterSuppressedIncrementalRendering"_s);
741 addIfSet(DidFirstPaintAfterSuppressedIncrementalRendering, "DidFirstPaintAfterSuppressedIncrementalRendering"_s);
742 addIfSet(ReachedSessionRestorationRenderTreeSizeThreshold, "ReachedSessionRestorationRenderTreeSizeThreshold"_s);
743 addIfSet(DidRenderSignificantAmountOfText, "DidRenderSignificantAmountOfText"_s);
744 addIfSet(DidFirstMeaningfulPaint, "DidFirstMeaningfulPaint"_s);
745
746 WEBFRAMELOADERCLIENT_RELEASE_LOG(Layout, "dispatchDidReachLayoutMilestone: dispatching DidReachLayoutMilestone (milestones=%{public}s)", builder.toString().utf8().data());
747#endif
748
749 // Send this after DidFirstLayout-specific calls since some clients expect to get those messages first.
750 webPage->dispatchDidReachLayoutMilestone(milestones);
751
752 if (milestones & DidFirstVisuallyNonEmptyLayout) {
753 ASSERT(!m_frame->isMainFrame() || webPage->corePage()->settings().suppressesIncrementalRendering() || m_didCompletePageTransition);
754 // FIXME: We should consider removing the old didFirstVisuallyNonEmptyLayoutForFrame API since this is doing double duty with the new didLayout API.
755 WEBFRAMELOADERCLIENT_RELEASE_LOG(Layout, "dispatchDidReachLayoutMilestone: dispatching DidFirstVisuallyNonEmptyLayoutForFrame");
756 webPage->injectedBundleLoaderClient().didFirstVisuallyNonEmptyLayoutForFrame(*webPage, m_frame, userData);
757 webPage->send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidFirstVisuallyNonEmptyLayoutForFrame(m_frame->frameID(), UserData(WebProcess::singleton().transformObjectsToHandles(userData.get()).get())));
758 }
759}
760
761void WebFrameLoaderClient::dispatchDidReachVisuallyNonEmptyState()
762{
763 if (!m_frame->page() || m_frame->page()->corePage()->settings().suppressesIncrementalRendering())
764 return;
765 ASSERT(m_frame->isMainFrame());
766 completePageTransitionIfNeeded();
767}
768
769void WebFrameLoaderClient::dispatchDidLayout()
770{
771 WebPage* webPage = m_frame->page();
772 if (!webPage)
773 return;
774
775 // Notify the bundle client.
776 webPage->injectedBundleLoaderClient().didLayoutForFrame(*webPage, m_frame);
777
778 webPage->recomputeShortCircuitHorizontalWheelEventsState();
779
780#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
781 webPage->updateSelectionAppearance();
782#endif
783
784 // NOTE: Unlike the other layout notifications, this does not notify the
785 // the UIProcess for every call.
786
787 if (m_frame.ptr() == &m_frame->page()->mainWebFrame()) {
788 // FIXME: Remove at the soonest possible time.
789 webPage->send(Messages::WebPageProxy::SetRenderTreeSize(webPage->renderTreeSize()));
790 webPage->mainFrameDidLayout();
791 }
792}

794Frame* WebFrameLoaderClient::dispatchCreatePage(const NavigationAction& navigationAction, NewFrameOpenerPolicy newFrameOpenerPolicy)
795{
796 WebPage* webPage = m_frame->page();
797 if (!webPage)
798 return nullptr;
799

801 WindowFeatures windowFeatures;
802 windowFeatures.noopener = newFrameOpenerPolicy == NewFrameOpenerPolicy::Suppress;
803 Page* newPage = webPage->corePage()->chrome().createWindow(*m_frame->coreFrame(), windowFeatures, navigationAction);
804 if (!newPage)

806
807 return &newPage->mainFrame();
808}

818
819void WebFrameLoaderClient::dispatchDecidePolicyForResponse(const ResourceResponse& response, const ResourceRequest& request, WebCore::PolicyCheckIdentifier identifier, const String& downloadAttribute, FramePolicyFunction&& function)
820{
821 auto* webPage = m_frame->page();
822 if (!webPage) {
823 WEBFRAMELOADERCLIENT_RELEASE_LOG(Network, "dispatchDecidePolicyForResponse: ignoring because there's no web page");
824 function(PolicyAction::Ignore, identifier);
825 return;
826 }
827
828 if (!request.url().string()) {
829 WEBFRAMELOADERCLIENT_RELEASE_LOG(Network, "dispatchDecidePolicyForResponse: continuing because the url string is null");
830 function(PolicyAction::Use, identifier);
831 return;
832 }
833
834 RefPtr<API::Object> userData;
835
836 // Notify the bundle client.
837 WKBundlePagePolicyAction policy = webPage->injectedBundlePolicyClient().decidePolicyForResponse(webPage, m_frame.ptr(), response, request, userData);
838 if (policy == WKBundlePagePolicyActionUse) {
839 WEBFRAMELOADERCLIENT_RELEASE_LOG(Network, "dispatchDecidePolicyForResponse: continuing because injected bundle says so");
840 function(PolicyAction::Use, identifier);
841 return;
842 }
843
844 bool canShowResponse = webPage->canShowResponse(response);
845
846 auto* coreFrame = m_frame->coreFrame();
847 auto* policyDocumentLoader = coreFrame ? coreFrame->loader().provisionalDocumentLoader() : nullptr;
848 auto navigationID = policyDocumentLoader ? static_cast<WebDocumentLoader&>(*policyDocumentLoader).navigationID() : 0;
849
850 auto protector = m_frame.copyRef();
851 uint64_t listenerID = m_frame->setUpPolicyListener(identifier, WTFMove(function), WebFrame::ForNavigationAction::No);
852 if (!webPage->send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DecidePolicyForResponse(m_frame->frameID(), m_frame->info(), identifier, navigationID, response, request, canShowResponse, downloadAttribute, listenerID, UserData(WebProcess::singleton().transformObjectsToHandles(userData.get()).get())))) {
853 WEBFRAMELOADERCLIENT_RELEASE_LOG(Network, "dispatchDecidePolicyForResponse: ignoring because WebPageProxy::DecidePolicyForResponse failed");
854 m_frame->didReceivePolicyDecision(listenerID, PolicyDecision { identifier, std::nullopt, PolicyAction::Ignore, 0, { }, { } });
855 }
856}
857
858void WebFrameLoaderClient::dispatchDecidePolicyForNewWindowAction(const NavigationAction& navigationAction, const ResourceRequest& request,
859 FormState* formState, const String& frameName, WebCore::PolicyCheckIdentifier identifier, FramePolicyFunction&& function)
860{
861 auto* webPage = m_frame->page();
862 if (!webPage) {
863 function(PolicyAction::Ignore, identifier);
864 return;
865 }
866
867 RefPtr<API::Object> userData;
868
869 auto action = InjectedBundleNavigationAction::create(m_frame.ptr(), navigationAction, formState);
870
871 // Notify the bundle client.
872 WKBundlePagePolicyAction policy = webPage->injectedBundlePolicyClient().decidePolicyForNewWindowAction(webPage, m_frame.ptr(), action.ptr(), request, frameName, userData);
873 if (policy == WKBundlePagePolicyActionUse) {
874 function(PolicyAction::Use, identifier);
875 return;
876 }
877
878 uint64_t listenerID = m_frame->setUpPolicyListener(identifier, WTFMove(function), WebFrame::ForNavigationAction::No);
879
880 NavigationActionData navigationActionData;
881 navigationActionData.navigationType = action->navigationType();
882 navigationActionData.modifiers = action->modifiers();
883 navigationActionData.mouseButton = action->mouseButton();
884 navigationActionData.syntheticClickType = action->syntheticClickType();
885 navigationActionData.clickLocationInRootViewCoordinates = action->clickLocationInRootViewCoordinates();
886 navigationActionData.userGestureTokenIdentifier = WebProcess::singleton().userGestureTokenIdentifier(navigationAction.userGestureToken());
887 navigationActionData.canHandleRequest = webPage->canHandleRequest(request);
888 navigationActionData.shouldOpenExternalURLsPolicy = navigationAction.shouldOpenExternalURLsPolicy();
889 navigationActionData.downloadAttribute = navigationAction.downloadAttribute();
890 navigationActionData.privateClickMeasurement = navigationAction.privateClickMeasurement();
891
892 webPage->send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DecidePolicyForNewWindowAction(m_frame->frameID(), m_frame->info(), identifier, navigationActionData, request,
893 frameName, listenerID, UserData(WebProcess::singleton().transformObjectsToHandles(userData.get()).get())));
894}
895
896void WebFrameLoaderClient::applyToDocumentLoader(WebsitePoliciesData&& websitePolicies)
897{
898 auto* coreFrame = m_frame->coreFrame();
899 if (!coreFrame)
900 return;
901 WebDocumentLoader* documentLoader = static_cast<WebDocumentLoader*>(coreFrame->loader().policyDocumentLoader());
902 if (!documentLoader)
903 documentLoader = static_cast<WebDocumentLoader*>(coreFrame->loader().provisionalDocumentLoader());
904 if (!documentLoader)
905 documentLoader = static_cast<WebDocumentLoader*>(coreFrame->loader().documentLoader());
906 if (!documentLoader)
907 return;
908
909 WebsitePoliciesData::applyToDocumentLoader(WTFMove(websitePolicies), *documentLoader);
910}

912WebCore::AllowsContentJavaScript WebFrameLoaderClient::allowsContentJavaScriptFromMostRecentNavigation() const

917
918void WebFrameLoaderClient::dispatchDecidePolicyForNavigationAction(const NavigationAction& navigationAction, const ResourceRequest& request, const ResourceResponse& redirectResponse,
919 FormState* formState, PolicyDecisionMode policyDecisionMode, WebCore::PolicyCheckIdentifier requestIdentifier, FramePolicyFunction&& function)
920{
921 auto* webPage = m_frame->page();
922 if (!webPage) {
923 WEBFRAMELOADERCLIENT_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "dispatchDecidePolicyForNavigationAction: ignoring because there's no web page");
924 function(PolicyAction::Ignore, requestIdentifier);
925 return;
926 }
927
928 LOG(Loading, "WebProcess %i - dispatchDecidePolicyForNavigationAction to request url %s", getCurrentProcessID(), request.url().string().utf8().data());
929
930 // Always ignore requests with empty URLs.
931 if (request.isEmpty()) {
932 WEBFRAMELOADERCLIENT_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "dispatchDecidePolicyForNavigationAction: ignoring because request is empty");
933 function(PolicyAction::Ignore, requestIdentifier);
934 return;
935 }
936
937 RefPtr<API::Object> userData;
938
939 Ref<InjectedBundleNavigationAction> action = InjectedBundleNavigationAction::create(m_frame.ptr(), navigationAction, formState);
940
941 // Notify the bundle client.
942 WKBundlePagePolicyAction policy = webPage->injectedBundlePolicyClient().decidePolicyForNavigationAction(webPage, m_frame.ptr(), action.ptr(), request, userData);
943 if (policy == WKBundlePagePolicyActionUse) {
944 WEBFRAMELOADERCLIENT_RELEASE_LOG(Network, "dispatchDecidePolicyForNavigationAction: Injected Bundle responded with PolicyAction::Use");
945 function(PolicyAction::Use, requestIdentifier);
946 return;
947 }
948
949 uint64_t listenerID = m_frame->setUpPolicyListener(requestIdentifier, WTFMove(function), WebFrame::ForNavigationAction::Yes);
950
951 ASSERT(navigationAction.requester());
952 auto requester = navigationAction.requester().value();
953
954 auto* requestingFrame = requester.globalFrameIdentifier().frameID ? WebProcess::singleton().webFrame(requester.globalFrameIdentifier().frameID) : nullptr;
955 std::optional<WebCore::FrameIdentifier> originatingFrameID;
956 std::optional<WebCore::FrameIdentifier> parentFrameID;
957 if (requestingFrame) {
958 originatingFrameID = requestingFrame->frameID();
959 if (auto* parentFrame = requestingFrame->parentFrame())
960 parentFrameID = parentFrame->frameID();
961 }
962
963 FrameInfoData originatingFrameInfoData {
964 navigationAction.initiatedByMainFrame() == InitiatedByMainFrame::Yes,
965 ResourceRequest { requester.url() },
966 requester.securityOrigin().data(),
967 WTFMove(originatingFrameID),
968 WTFMove(parentFrameID),
969 };
970
971 std::optional<WebPageProxyIdentifier> originatingPageID;
972 if (auto& pageID = requester.globalFrameIdentifier().pageID) {
973 if (auto* webPage = WebProcess::singleton().webPage(pageID))
974 originatingPageID = webPage->webPageProxyIdentifier();
975 }
976
977 NavigationActionData navigationActionData;
978 navigationActionData.navigationType = action->navigationType();
979 navigationActionData.modifiers = action->modifiers();
980 navigationActionData.mouseButton = action->mouseButton();
981 navigationActionData.syntheticClickType = action->syntheticClickType();
982 navigationActionData.clickLocationInRootViewCoordinates = action->clickLocationInRootViewCoordinates();
983 navigationActionData.userGestureTokenIdentifier = WebProcess::singleton().userGestureTokenIdentifier(navigationAction.userGestureToken());
984 navigationActionData.canHandleRequest = webPage->canHandleRequest(request);
985 navigationActionData.shouldOpenExternalURLsPolicy = navigationAction.shouldOpenExternalURLsPolicy();
986 navigationActionData.downloadAttribute = navigationAction.downloadAttribute();
987 navigationActionData.isRedirect = !redirectResponse.isNull();
988 navigationActionData.treatAsSameOriginNavigation = navigationAction.treatAsSameOriginNavigation();
989 navigationActionData.hasOpenedFrames = navigationAction.hasOpenedFrames();
990 navigationActionData.openedByDOMWithOpener = navigationAction.openedByDOMWithOpener();
991 if (auto& requester = navigationAction.requester())
992 navigationActionData.requesterOrigin = requester->securityOrigin().data();
993 navigationActionData.targetBackForwardItemIdentifier = navigationAction.targetBackForwardItemIdentifier();
994 navigationActionData.sourceBackForwardItemIdentifier = navigationAction.sourceBackForwardItemIdentifier();
995 navigationActionData.lockHistory = navigationAction.lockHistory();
996 navigationActionData.lockBackForwardList = navigationAction.lockBackForwardList();
997 navigationActionData.privateClickMeasurement = navigationAction.privateClickMeasurement();
998
999 auto* coreFrame = m_frame->coreFrame();
1000 if (!coreFrame)
1001 return function(PolicyAction::Ignore, requestIdentifier);
1002 WebDocumentLoader* documentLoader = static_cast<WebDocumentLoader*>(coreFrame->loader().policyDocumentLoader());
1003 if (!documentLoader) {
1004 // FIXME: When we receive a redirect after the navigation policy has been decided for the initial request,
1005 // the provisional load's DocumentLoader needs to receive navigation policy decisions. We need a better model for this state.
1006 documentLoader = static_cast<WebDocumentLoader*>(coreFrame->loader().provisionalDocumentLoader());
1007 }
1008 if (!documentLoader)
1009 documentLoader = static_cast<WebDocumentLoader*>(coreFrame->loader().documentLoader());
1010
1011 navigationActionData.clientRedirectSourceForHistory = documentLoader->clientRedirectSourceForHistory();
1012
1013 // Notify the UIProcess.
1014 auto protector = makeRef(*coreFrame);
1015
1016 if (policyDecisionMode == PolicyDecisionMode::Synchronous) {
1017 PolicyDecision policyDecision;
1018
1019 if (!webPage->sendSync(Messages::WebPageProxy::DecidePolicyForNavigationActionSync(m_frame->frameID(), m_frame->isMainFrame(), m_frame->info(), requestIdentifier, documentLoader->navigationID(), navigationActionData, originatingFrameInfoData, originatingPageID, navigationAction.resourceRequest(), request, IPC::FormDataReference { request.httpBody() }, redirectResponse, UserData(WebProcess::singleton().transformObjectsToHandles(userData.get()).get())), Messages::WebPageProxy::DecidePolicyForNavigationActionSync::Reply(policyDecision))) {
1020 WEBFRAMELOADERCLIENT_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "dispatchDecidePolicyForNavigationAction: ignoring because of failing to send sync IPC");
1021 m_frame->didReceivePolicyDecision(listenerID, PolicyDecision { requestIdentifier, std::nullopt, PolicyAction::Ignore, 0, { }, { } });
1022 return;
1023 }
1024
1025 WEBFRAMELOADERCLIENT_RELEASE_LOG(Network, "dispatchDecidePolicyForNavigationAction: Got policyAction %u from sync IPC", (unsigned)policyDecision.policyAction);
1026 m_frame->didReceivePolicyDecision(listenerID, PolicyDecision { policyDecision.identifier, policyDecision.isNavigatingToAppBoundDomain, policyDecision.policyAction, 0, policyDecision.downloadID, { }});
1027 return;
1028 }
1029
1030 ASSERT(policyDecisionMode == PolicyDecisionMode::Asynchronous);
1031 if (!webPage->send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DecidePolicyForNavigationActionAsync(m_frame->frameID(), m_frame->info(), requestIdentifier, documentLoader->navigationID(), navigationActionData, originatingFrameInfoData, originatingPageID, navigationAction.resourceRequest(), request, IPC::FormDataReference { request.httpBody() }, redirectResponse, UserData(WebProcess::singleton().transformObjectsToHandles(userData.get()).get()), listenerID))) {
1032 WEBFRAMELOADERCLIENT_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "dispatchDecidePolicyForNavigationAction: ignoring because of failing to send async IPC");
1033 m_frame->didReceivePolicyDecision(listenerID, PolicyDecision { requestIdentifier, std::nullopt, PolicyAction::Ignore, 0, { }, { } });
1034 }
1035}

1072void WebFrameLoaderClient::dispatchWillSubmitForm(FormState& formState, CompletionHandler<void()>&& completionHandler)
1073{
1074 WebPage* webPage = m_frame->page();
1075 if (!webPage) {
1076 completionHandler();
1077 return;
1078 }
1079
1080 auto& form = formState.form();
1081
1082 auto* sourceCoreFrame = formState.sourceDocument().frame();
1083 if (!sourceCoreFrame)
1084 return completionHandler();
1085 auto* sourceFrame = WebFrame::fromCoreFrame(*sourceCoreFrame);
1086 if (!sourceFrame)
1087 return completionHandler();
1088
1089 auto& values = formState.textFieldValues();
1090
1091 RefPtr<API::Object> userData;
1092 webPage->injectedBundleFormClient().willSubmitForm(webPage, &form, m_frame.ptr(), sourceFrame, values, userData);
1093
1094 uint64_t listenerID = m_frame->setUpWillSubmitFormListener(WTFMove(completionHandler));
1095
1096 webPage->send(Messages::WebPageProxy::WillSubmitForm(m_frame->frameID(), sourceFrame->frameID(), values, listenerID, UserData(WebProcess::singleton().transformObjectsToHandles(userData.get()).get())));
1097}

1149
1150void WebFrameLoaderClient::committedLoad(DocumentLoader* loader, const uint8_t* data, int length)
1151{
1152 if (!m_pluginView)
1153 loader->commitData(data, length);
1154
1155 // If the document is a stand-alone media document, now is the right time to cancel the WebKit load.
1156 // FIXME: This code should be shared across all ports. <http://webkit.org/b/48762>.
1157#if ENABLE(VIDEO)
1158 if (is<MediaDocument>(m_frame->coreFrame()->document()))
1159 loader->cancelMainResourceLoad(pluginWillHandleLoadError(loader->response()));
1160#endif
1161
1162 // Calling commitData did not create the plug-in view.
1163 if (!m_pluginView)
1164 return;
1165
1166 if (!m_hasSentResponseToPluginView) {
1167 m_pluginView->manualLoadDidReceiveResponse(loader->response());
1168 // manualLoadDidReceiveResponse sets up a new stream to the plug-in. on a full-page plug-in, a failure in
1169 // setting up this stream can cause the main document load to be cancelled, setting m_pluginView
1170 // to null
1171 if (!m_pluginView)
1172 return;
1173 m_hasSentResponseToPluginView = true;
1174 }
1175 m_pluginView->manualLoadDidReceiveData(data, length);
1176}
1177
1178void WebFrameLoaderClient::finishedLoading(DocumentLoader* loader)
1179{
1180 if (!m_pluginView) {
1181 if (m_frameHasCustomContentProvider) {
1182 WebPage* webPage = m_frame->page();
1183 if (!webPage)
1184 return;
1185
1186 RefPtr<SharedBuffer> mainResourceData = loader->mainResourceData();
1187 IPC::DataReference dataReference(mainResourceData ? mainResourceData->data() : nullptr, mainResourceData ? mainResourceData->size() : 0);
1188 webPage->send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidFinishLoadingDataForCustomContentProvider(loader->response().suggestedFilename(), dataReference));
1189 }
1190
1191 return;
1192 }
1193
1194 // If we just received an empty response without any data, we won't have sent a response to the plug-in view.
1195 // Make sure to do this before calling manualLoadDidFinishLoading.
1196 if (!m_hasSentResponseToPluginView) {
1197 m_pluginView->manualLoadDidReceiveResponse(loader->response());
1198
1199 // Protect against the above call nulling out the plug-in (by trying to cancel the load for example).
1200 if (!m_pluginView)
1201 return;
1202 }
1203
1204 m_pluginView->manualLoadDidFinishLoading();
1205 m_pluginView = nullptr;
1206 m_hasSentResponseToPluginView = false;
1207}
1208
1209void WebFrameLoaderClient::updateGlobalHistory()
1210{
1211 WebPage* webPage = m_frame->page();
1212 if (!webPage)
1213 return;
1214
1215 DocumentLoader* loader = m_frame->coreFrame()->loader().documentLoader();
1216
1217 WebNavigationDataStore data;
1218 data.url = loader->url().string();
1219 // FIXME: Use direction of title.
1220 data.title = loader->title().string;
1221 data.originalRequest = loader->originalRequestCopy();
1222 data.response = loader->response();
1223
1224 webPage->send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidNavigateWithNavigationData(data, m_frame->frameID()));
1225}
1226
1227void WebFrameLoaderClient::updateGlobalHistoryRedirectLinks()
1228{
1229 WebPage* webPage = m_frame->page();
1230 if (!webPage)
1231 return;
1232
1233 DocumentLoader* loader = m_frame->coreFrame()->loader().documentLoader();
1234 ASSERT(loader->unreachableURL().isEmpty());
1235
1236 // Client redirect
1237 if (!loader->clientRedirectSourceForHistory().isNull()) {
1238 webPage->send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidPerformClientRedirect(
1239 loader->clientRedirectSourceForHistory(), loader->clientRedirectDestinationForHistory(), m_frame->frameID()));
1240 }
1241
1242 // Server redirect
1243 if (!loader->serverRedirectSourceForHistory().isNull()) {
1244 webPage->send(Messages::WebPageProxy::DidPerformServerRedirect(
1245 loader->serverRedirectSourceForHistory(), loader->serverRedirectDestinationForHistory(), m_frame->frameID()));
1246 }
1247}
1248
1249bool WebFrameLoaderClient::shouldGoToHistoryItem(HistoryItem& item) const
1250{
1251 WebPage* webPage = m_frame->page();
1252 if (!webPage)
1253 return false;
1254 webPage->send(Messages::WebPageProxy::WillGoToBackForwardListItem(item.identifier(), item.isInBackForwardCache()));
1255 return true;
1256}

1344bool WebFrameLoaderClient::shouldFallBack(const ResourceError& error) const
1345{
1346 static NeverDestroyed<const ResourceError> cancelledError(this->cancelledError(ResourceRequest()));
1347 static NeverDestroyed<const ResourceError> pluginWillHandleLoadError(this->pluginWillHandleLoadError(ResourceResponse()));
1348
1349 if (error.errorCode() == cancelledError.get().errorCode() && error.domain() == cancelledError.get().domain())
1350 return false;
1351
1352 if (error.errorCode() == pluginWillHandleLoadError.get().errorCode() && error.domain() == pluginWillHandleLoadError.get().domain())
1353 return false;
1354
1355 return true;
1356}

1400#else

1404
1405void WebFrameLoaderClient::restoreViewState()
1406{
1407#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
1408 Frame& frame = *m_frame->coreFrame();
1409 HistoryItem* currentItem = frame.loader().history().currentItem();
1410 if (FrameView* view = frame.view()) {
1411 if (m_frame->isMainFrame())
1412 m_frame->page()->restorePageState(*currentItem);
1413 else if (!view->wasScrolledByUser())
1414 view->setScrollPosition(currentItem->scrollPosition());
1415 }
1416#else
1417 // Inform the UI process of the scale factor.
1418 double scaleFactor = m_frame->coreFrame()->loader().history().currentItem()->pageScaleFactor();
1419
1420 // A scale factor of 0 means the history item has the default scale factor, thus we do not need to update it.
1421 if (scaleFactor)
1422 m_frame->page()->send(Messages::WebPageProxy::PageScaleFactorDidChange(scaleFactor));
1423
1424 // FIXME: This should not be necessary. WebCore should be correctly invalidating
1425 // the view on restores from the back/forward cache.
1426 if (m_frame->page() && m_frame.ptr() == &m_frame->page()->mainWebFrame())
1427 m_frame->page()->drawingArea()->setNeedsDisplay();
1428#endif
1429}

1497void WebFrameLoaderClient::transitionToCommittedFromCachedFrame(CachedFrame*)
1498{
1499 const ResourceResponse& response = m_frame->coreFrame()->loader().documentLoader()->response();
1500 m_frameHasCustomContentProvider = m_frame->isMainFrame() && m_frame->page()->shouldUseCustomContentProviderForResponse(response);
1501 m_frameCameFromBackForwardCache = true;
1502}
1503
1504void WebFrameLoaderClient::transitionToCommittedForNewPage()
1505{
1506 WebPage* webPage = m_frame->page();
1507
1508 bool isMainFrame = m_frame->isMainFrame();
1509 bool shouldUseFixedLayout = isMainFrame && webPage->useFixedLayout();
1510 bool shouldDisableScrolling = isMainFrame && !webPage->mainFrameIsScrollable();
1511 bool shouldHideScrollbars = shouldDisableScrolling;
1512 IntRect fixedVisibleContentRect;
1513
1514#if USE(COORDINATED_GRAPHICS)
1515 if (m_frame->coreFrame()->view())
1516 fixedVisibleContentRect = m_frame->coreFrame()->view()->fixedVisibleContentRect();
1517 if (shouldUseFixedLayout)
1518 shouldHideScrollbars = true;
1519#endif
1520
1521 m_frameHasCustomContentProvider = isMainFrame
1522 && m_frame->coreFrame()->loader().documentLoader()
1523 && webPage->shouldUseCustomContentProviderForResponse(m_frame->coreFrame()->loader().documentLoader()->response());
1524 m_frameCameFromBackForwardCache = false;
1525
1526 ScrollbarMode defaultScrollbarMode = shouldHideScrollbars ? ScrollbarAlwaysOff : ScrollbarAuto;
1527
1528 ScrollbarMode horizontalScrollbarMode = webPage->alwaysShowsHorizontalScroller() ? ScrollbarAlwaysOn : defaultScrollbarMode;
1529 ScrollbarMode verticalScrollbarMode = webPage->alwaysShowsVerticalScroller() ? ScrollbarAlwaysOn : defaultScrollbarMode;
1530
1531 bool horizontalLock = shouldHideScrollbars || webPage->alwaysShowsHorizontalScroller();
1532 bool verticalLock = shouldHideScrollbars || webPage->alwaysShowsVerticalScroller();
1533
1534 m_frame->coreFrame()->createView(webPage->size(), webPage->backgroundColor(),
1535 webPage->fixedLayoutSize(), fixedVisibleContentRect, shouldUseFixedLayout,
1536 horizontalScrollbarMode, horizontalLock, verticalScrollbarMode, verticalLock);
1537
1538 RefPtr<FrameView> view = m_frame->coreFrame()->view();
1539 if (int width = webPage->minimumSizeForAutoLayout().width()) {
1540 int height = std::max(webPage->minimumSizeForAutoLayout().height(), 1);
1541 view->enableFixedWidthAutoSizeMode(true, { width, height });
1542
1543 if (webPage->autoSizingShouldExpandToViewHeight())
1544 view->setAutoSizeFixedMinimumHeight(webPage->size().height());
1545 }
1546
1547 IntSize sizeToContentAutoSizeMaximumSize = webPage->sizeToContentAutoSizeMaximumSize();
1548 if (sizeToContentAutoSizeMaximumSize.width() && sizeToContentAutoSizeMaximumSize.height()) {
1549 if (isMainFrame)
1550 view->enableSizeToContentAutoSizeMode(true, sizeToContentAutoSizeMaximumSize);
1551
1552 if (webPage->autoSizingShouldExpandToViewHeight())
1553 view->setAutoSizeFixedMinimumHeight(webPage->size().height());
1554 }
1555
1556 if (auto viewportSizeForViewportUnits = webPage->viewportSizeForCSSViewportUnits())
1557 view->setViewportSizeForCSSViewportUnits(*viewportSizeForViewportUnits);
1558 view->setProhibitsScrolling(shouldDisableScrolling);
1559 view->setVisualUpdatesAllowedByClient(!webPage->shouldExtendIncrementalRenderingSuppression());
1560#if PLATFORM(COCOA)
1561 auto* drawingArea = webPage->drawingArea();
1562 view->setViewExposedRect(drawingArea->viewExposedRect());
1563 if (isMainFrame)
1564 view->setDelegatesScrolling(drawingArea->usesDelegatedScrolling());
1565
1566 webPage->corePage()->setDelegatesScaling(drawingArea->usesDelegatedPageScaling());
1567#endif
1568
1569 if (webPage->scrollPinningBehavior() != DoNotPin)
1570 view->setScrollPinningBehavior(webPage->scrollPinningBehavior());
1571
1572#if USE(COORDINATED_GRAPHICS)
1573 if (shouldUseFixedLayout) {
1574 view->setDelegatesScrolling(shouldUseFixedLayout);
1575 view->setPaintsEntireContents(shouldUseFixedLayout);
1576 return;
1577 }
1578#endif
1579}
1580
1581void WebFrameLoaderClient::didRestoreFromBackForwardCache()
1582{
1583 m_frameCameFromBackForwardCache = true;
1584}

1589 // rendered in the UIProcess.
1590 return !m_frameHasCustomContentProvider;
1591}

1598RefPtr<Frame> WebFrameLoaderClient::createFrame(const String& name, HTMLFrameOwnerElement& ownerElement)
1599{
1600 auto* webPage = m_frame->page();
1601
1602 auto subframe = WebFrame::createSubframe(webPage, name, &ownerElement);
1603 auto* coreSubframe = subframe->coreFrame();
1604 if (!coreSubframe)
1605 return nullptr;
1606
1607 // The creation of the frame may have run arbitrary JavaScript that removed it from the page already.
1608 if (!coreSubframe->page())
1609 return nullptr;
1610
1611 return coreSubframe;
1612}

1614RefPtr<Widget> WebFrameLoaderClient::createPlugin(const IntSize&, HTMLPlugInElement& pluginElement, const URL& url, const Vector<String>& paramNames, const Vector<String>& paramValues, const String& mimeType, bool loadManually)
1615{
1616 ASSERT(paramNames.size() == paramValues.size());
1617 ASSERT(m_frame->page());
1618
1619 Plugin::Parameters parameters;
1620 parameters.url = url;
1621 parameters.names = paramNames;
1622 parameters.values = paramValues;
1623 parameters.mimeType = mimeType;
1624 parameters.isFullFramePlugin = loadManually;
1625 parameters.shouldUseManualLoader = parameters.isFullFramePlugin && !m_frameCameFromBackForwardCache;
1626#if PLATFORM(COCOA)
1627 parameters.layerHostingMode = m_frame->page()->layerHostingMode();
1628#endif
1629
1630#if ENABLE(NETSCAPE_PLUGIN_API)
1631 auto plugin = m_frame->page()->createPlugin(m_frame.ptr(), &pluginElement, parameters, parameters.mimeType);
1632 if (!plugin)
1633 return nullptr;
1634
1635 return PluginView::create(pluginElement, plugin.releaseNonNull(), parameters);
1636#else
1637 UNUSED_PARAM(pluginElement);
1638 return nullptr;
1639#endif
1640}

1643{
1644 m_pluginView = static_cast<PluginView*>(&pluginWidget);
1645}

1666
1667static bool pluginSupportsExtension(const PluginData& pluginData, const String& extension)
1668{
1669 ASSERT(extension.convertToASCIILowercase() == extension);
1670 for (auto& type : pluginData.webVisibleMimeTypes()) {
1671 if (type.extensions.contains(extension))
1672 return true;
1673 }
1674 return false;
1675}
1676
1677ObjectContentType WebFrameLoaderClient::objectContentType(const URL& url, const String& mimeTypeIn)
1678{
1679 // FIXME: This should eventually be merged with WebCore::FrameLoader::defaultObjectContentType.
1680
1681 String mimeType = mimeTypeIn;
1682 if (mimeType.isEmpty()) {
1683 auto path = url.path();
1684 auto dotPosition = path.reverseFind('.');
1685 if (dotPosition == notFound)
1686 return ObjectContentType::Frame;
1687 auto extension = path.substring(dotPosition + 1).convertToASCIILowercase();
1688
1689 // Try to guess the MIME type from the extension.
1690 mimeType = MIMETypeRegistry::mimeTypeForExtension(extension);
1691 if (mimeType.isEmpty()) {
1692 // Check if there's a plug-in around that can handle the extension.
1693 if (auto* webPage = m_frame->page()) {
1694 if (pluginSupportsExtension(webPage->corePage()->pluginData(), extension))
1695 return ObjectContentType::PlugIn;
1696 }
1697 return ObjectContentType::Frame;
1698 }
1699 }
1700
1701 if (MIMETypeRegistry::isSupportedImageMIMEType(mimeType))
1702 return ObjectContentType::Image;
1703
1704 if (WebPage* webPage = m_frame->page()) {
1705 auto allowedPluginTypes = webFrame().coreFrame()->arePluginsEnabled()
1706 ? PluginData::AllPlugins : PluginData::OnlyApplicationPlugins;
1707 if (webPage->corePage()->pluginData().supportsMimeType(mimeType, allowedPluginTypes))
1708 return ObjectContentType::PlugIn;
1709 }
1710
1711 if (MIMETypeRegistry::isSupportedNonImageMIMEType(mimeType))
1712 return ObjectContentType::Frame;
1713
1714#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
1715 // iOS can render PDF in <object>/<embed> via PDFDocumentImage.
1716 if (MIMETypeRegistry::isPDFOrPostScriptMIMEType(mimeType))
1717 return ObjectContentType::Image;
1718#endif
1719
1720 return ObjectContentType::None;
1721}
1722
1723String WebFrameLoaderClient::overrideMediaType() const
1724{
1725 if (auto* page = m_frame->page())
1726 return page->overriddenMediaType();
1727
1728 return String();
1729}

1731void WebFrameLoaderClient::dispatchDidClearWindowObjectInWorld(DOMWrapperWorld& world)
1732{
1733 WebPage* webPage = m_frame->page();
1734 if (!webPage)
1735 return;
1736
1737#if ENABLE(IPC_TESTING_API)

1739 IPCTestingAPI::inject(*webPage, m_frame.get(), world);
1740#endif
1741
1742 webPage->injectedBundleLoaderClient().didClearWindowObjectForFrame(*webPage, m_frame, world);
1743
1744 WebAutomationSessionProxy* automationSessionProxy = WebProcess::singleton().automationSessionProxy();
1745 if (automationSessionProxy && world.isNormal())
1746 automationSessionProxy->didClearWindowObjectForFrame(m_frame);
1747}

1873void WebFrameLoaderClient::prefetchDNS(const String& hostname)
1874{
1875 WebProcess::singleton().prefetchDNS(hostname);
1876}
1877
1878void WebFrameLoaderClient::sendH2Ping(const URL& url, CompletionHandler<void(Expected<Seconds, ResourceError>&&)>&& completionHandler)
1879{
1880 WebPage* webPage = m_frame->page();
1881 if (!webPage)
1882 return completionHandler(makeUnexpected(internalError(url)));
1883
1884 NetworkResourceLoadParameters parameters;
1885 parameters.request = ResourceRequest(url);
1886 parameters.identifier = WebLoaderStrategy::generateLoadIdentifier();
1887 parameters.webPageProxyID = webPage->webPageProxyIdentifier();
1888 parameters.webPageID = webPage->identifier();
1889 parameters.webFrameID = m_frame->frameID();
1890 parameters.parentPID = presentingApplicationPID();
1891#if HAVE(AUDIT_TOKEN)
1892 parameters.networkProcessAuditToken = WebProcess::singleton().ensureNetworkProcessConnection().networkProcessAuditToken();
1893#endif
1894 parameters.shouldPreconnectOnly = PreconnectOnly::Yes;
1895 parameters.options.destination = FetchOptions::Destination::EmptyString;
1896#if ENABLE(APP_BOUND_DOMAINS)
1897 parameters.isNavigatingToAppBoundDomain = m_frame->isTopFrameNavigatingToAppBoundDomain();
1898#endif
1899 WebProcess::singleton().ensureNetworkProcessConnection().connection().sendWithAsyncReply(Messages::NetworkConnectionToWebProcess::SendH2Ping(parameters), WTFMove(completionHandler));
1900}

1911void WebFrameLoaderClient::getLoadDecisionForIcons(const Vector<std::pair<WebCore::LinkIcon&, uint64_t>>& icons)
1912{
1913 auto* webPage = m_frame->page();
1914 if (!webPage)
1915 return;
1916
1917 for (auto& icon : icons)
1918 webPage->send(Messages::WebPageProxy::GetLoadDecisionForIcon(icon.first, CallbackID::fromInteger(icon.second)));
1919}

1947void WebFrameLoaderClient::notifyPageOfAppBoundBehavior()
1948{
